title: 11/04: Weekend Recap - Julio Scored! (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
What stood out from Sunday's games? First we'll tell you the big news (2:30) and discuss injuries to Chris Carson and A.J. Green before we get into our Winners (8:15) like Duke Johnson and Dalvin Cook and Losers (15:00) like Mark Ingram and Kenny Golladay ... Worryometer (23:03) for John Brown, Tarik Cohen and more. Buy or Sell (26:48) for Big Ben, Keenan Allen and more. And a look at the leaderboard (32:34) at each position as Ryan Fitzpatrick and Adam Humphries were among this week's standouts ... We review each game and give our Fantasy takes (40:10) ... Your emails at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
